The '''2016 Oceania Women's Sevens Championship''' was the sixth [[Oceania Women's Sevens]] tournament. It was held in [[Suva]], Fiji on 11–12 November 2016.<ref name=or-2016/>

Australia won the tournament as they won all six pool games to record the teams third [[Oceania Women's Sevens]] title

==Teams==
Participating nations for the 2016 tournament are:
* {{ruw7|Australia}}
* {{ruw7|Cook Islands}}
* {{ruw7|Fiji}}
* {{ruw7|Papua New Guinea}}
* {{ruw7|Samoa}}
* {{ruw7|Solomon Islands}}
* {{ruw7|Tonga}}

