'''Petit-Goâve Football Club''' (formerly '''Association Sportive Petit-Goâve''') is a professional [[football (soccer)|football]] club based in [[Haiti]]. As of 2015, they play in the top flight league of Haiti. 

==History==
The club was founded in 2011 as ''Association Sportive Petit-Goâve'' before undergoing a change in 2014 to its current name.<ref>[http://www.rsssf.com/tablesh/haiti2014.html Haiti: Championnat National D1 2014]</ref>

